gpsTimeoutHandler

remotelyDisabled

private static java.lang.Boolean remotelyDisabled
This keeps track of whether another plugin has remotely disabled scanning. For example, the location clustering plugin can disable the GPS plugin if the user is determined to be stationary.

pendingRemoteDisable

private static java.lang.Boolean pendingRemoteDisable
This keeps track of whether another plugin has requested that this plugin be disabled. We use this so that a plugin can request that this plugin be disabled after the next scan completes, rather than having other plugins disable the plugin immediately.
